headline: Cold Is Winning the Coffee Wars at Starbucks
summary: Starbucks’s business is going cold.  The trend extends beyond the U.S., with 60% of the chain’s global sales represented by cold espressos, fruity Refreshers, iced matcha and chilled tea lattes.  “Cold isn’t just growing, it’s reshaping the menu,” Starbucks said Thursday.
